{"lemma":"أَقْمَرانِ","slug":"أَقْمَرانِ","root":"ق.م.ر","root_slug":"ق-م-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ق-م-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36208"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%B1%D8%A7%D9%86%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36208","headword_ar":"اَقْمَرُ","root":"qmr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Of a colour inclining to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xuDorap","text_ar":"خُضْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a dull"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dingy"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dusky white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely white:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IKtt:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamoraA='u","text_ar":"قَمْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumorN","text_ar":"قُمْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.) You say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimaArN A^aqomaru","text_ar":"حِمَارٌ اَقْمَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An ass of the colour termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumorap","text_ar":"قُمْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a white ass:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataAnN qamoraA='u","text_ar":"اَتَانٌ قَمْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a she-ass of the colour termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qumorap","text_ar":"قُمْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a white she-ass."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) The Arabs say, that when the sky appears of the hue of the belly of a she-ass of this colour, it is most abundant in rain. (TA.) Also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN A^aqomaru","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ اَقْمَرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A moon-coloured horse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbN A^aqomaru","text_ar":"سَحَابٌ اَقْمَرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cloud,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clouds, of a white colour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely bright, by reason of the abundance of water therein:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [hence]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of water"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapN qamoraA='u","text_ar":"لَيْلَةٌ قَمْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqomirapN","text_ar":"مُقْمِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqomirN","text_ar":"مُقْمِرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qamirapN","text_ar":"قَمِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAar, K,) which last is held by ISd, to be a kind of rel. n., or possessive epithet, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A moon-lit night; a night in which the moon shines:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bright, night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a white night."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) IAar, mentions"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolN qamoraA='u","text_ar":"لَيْلٌ قَمْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but ISd, says this is strange, and I think, he adds, that by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lyl","text_ar":"ليل"},{"kind":"text","text":"he means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lylp","text_ar":"ليلة"},{"kind":"text","text":", or that he makes"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lyl","text_ar":"ليل"},{"kind":"text","text":"fem. as a pl. (TA.) You also say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolapu AlqamoraA='i","text_ar":"لَيْلَةُ القَمْرَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The night of moonlight:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, A, Mgh:) for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlqamoraA='u","text_ar":"القَمْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the moonlight."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, A, Mgh, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEadNnaA fiY AlqamoraA='i","text_ar":"قَعَدٌنَا فِى القَمْرَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We sat in the moonlight."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atoyotuhu fiY AlqamoraA='i","text_ar":"اَتْيْتُهُ فِى القَمْرَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him in the moonlight"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajohN A^aqamaru","text_ar":"وَجْهٌ اَقَمَرُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A face likened to the moon"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in respect of whiteness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","Msb","IKtt","A","IAar","TA","Lth","Mgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}